review.reviewBody: I've ordered from here multiple times and never been disappointed, but I ordered the QSA salad today with grilled chicken and WOW the chicken was so good??? So tender and juicy??? Even at more expensive restaurants I kind of expect chicken to be rubbery and overcooked (or let's be real: microwaved) at this point because it's become so common, but the chicken in this QSA salad was fantastic! The avocado was also great (nice and soft, not underripe or a giant brown spot like so many places give you nowadays). Tomatoes were nice and fresh too, not squishy at all. Gotta say I'm really, really impressed by the quality of this, especially for $15. I'll definitely be ordering this again, thanks CG staff!
No taste only spice. Never ordering again
I order from this place very often and they never disappoint. One of the best Indian food so far in this city. Absolutely love it
